---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="The philosophy behind Archie.">

  <div class="about-outer fade-up">
    <div class="glass-card about-card">
      <div class="about-deco"></div>
      <article class="about-article">

        <section class="about-section">
          <h1>Archie.</h1>
          <div class="about-body">
            <p>The name is a whisper from the woodlands, taken from <em>Myosotis sylvatica</em>.</p>
            <p>To the world, it is known simply as the <strong>Forget-Me-Not</strong>. A small, unassuming blue flower that carries a weight far heavier than its petals: a plea against oblivion.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2>The Philosophy</h2>
          <div class="about-body">
            <p>In the Victorian language of flowers, the Forget-Me-Not symbolizes true love, faithfulness, and <em>memories that never fade</em>.</p>
            <p>That is the sole purpose of this space.</p>
            <p>It is not a garden to be tended, but a <strong>Sanctuary</strong>. A place to keep the moments that matter, freezing them in digital amber so they are not washed away by time.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="about-quote-wrap">
          <blockquote class="about-quote">
            "Silent as the blue flower,<br/>loud as the memory it holds."
          </blockquote>
        </div>

      </article>
    </div>
    <div class="enduring-label">ENDURING MEMORIES</div>
  </div>

</Base>

<style is:global>
  /* FIXED: Gunakan is:global agar CSS bisa apply ke semua elemen */
  .about-outer { 
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-card {
    padding: 2.75rem 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-deco {
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    right: -40px;
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    background: rgba(100, 149, 237, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(40px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .about-article {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  /* FIXED: Gunakan CSS variables dari global */
  .about-section h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  
  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  
  .about-body em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  
  .about-body strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .about-divider {
    width: 64px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--blue-border);
  }
  
  .about-quote-wrap {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .enduring-label {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-mute);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-card {
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-quote {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>